      <h4>Brief</h4>
      <p>TrueSpirit is a new internet retailer for schools and parents who want a modern school uniform for K-12 children. Unlike traditional suppliers, TrueSpirit encourages visitors to express their tastes with some limits.</p>
      <h4>Challenge</h4>
      <p>TrueSprit wants to create an appropriate experience for their target customer that could be delivered via iPad as the primary delivery channel.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-4 padding-lr-30">
      <h4>Client</h4>
      <p>Project for User Experience Design Immersive at General Assembly, Sydney 2014</p>
      <h4>Duration</h4>
      <p>2 weeks</p>
      <h4>Team</h4>
      <p>Deepa Dhupalia</br>
        James Feng</br>
        Sara Michelazzo</br></p>
      </div>

