        <h4>My Role</h4>
        <p>Realize sketches for all pages, realize wireframes in Omnigraffle, realize an early-prototype in InVision, realize a mockup for the home page, improve and update user flows and sitemaps, execute design iterations, provide innovative ways to communicate our design.</p>
        <h4>Tools</h4>
        <p>Omnigraffle, Photoshop CC, Excel, Sharpies &amp; paper.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

