        <h4>COMPETITIVE ANALYSIS  &amp; RESEARCH</h4>
        <p>The competitor analysis involved both school uniforms e-commerce and fashion e-commerce. This research helped us to understand what the competitors are doing and what they are not doing in order to define a strategy.</p>
        <p><strong>School uniform e-commerce analyzed:</strong> Your Uniform Shop, School Uniform Australia, Made for School, Yeroga Uniforms.</br><strong>Fashion e-commerce analyzed:</strong>  Uniqlo, Polyvore, Net a porter, Yoox, Asos.</p>     
      </div>
    </div>

