    <!-- USABILITY TESTING -->
    <div class="row blockPadding-50-top">
      <div class="col-sm-8 padding-lr-30">
        <h4>USABILITY TESTING</h4>
        <p>The prototype has been tested on 3 people thorough a Gorilla Testing.</p>
        <p><strong>Pain points:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>We expected picture to zoom but user expected it to be a link to go to the details page dropdown menu and filter (colors, prices).</li>
          <li>One user would have saved his profile if it didn't include saving his credit card details.</li>
          <li>User went to sales button to find a polo shirt rather than top navigation bar.</li>
          <li>2/3 users could not find the alternative views (e.g. gallery versus list).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div> 

